<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 lái a wǒ men xiàng shén chàng xīn gē, lái a wǒ men xiàng shén chàng zàn měi gē,
 yīn tā ài nǐ yě ài wǒ, wàn yǒu yě jiāng tā de ài shù shuō,
 yīn tā běn wèi shàn, tā de cí ài yǒng yuǎn zhǎng cún.
 tiān shàng de rì yuè xīng chén, de shàng de rén, zàn měi bù jǐn, zàn měi bù jǐn.
 hā lì lù yà yé hé huá zuò wáng, hā lì lù yà xiàng hǎi dǎo huān xīn,
 hā lì lù yà xiàng shén lái gē chàng, tiān de yě tóng shēng shuō ā mén! ā mén!</lyrics>
<title>lái a wǒ men xiàng shén chàng xīn gē 迦南123</title>
<hymn_number>123</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
</song>